51 bool pilz_industrial_motion_planner::PlanningContextLoaderCIRC::loadContext(
52  planning_interface::PlanningContextPtr& planning_context, const std::string& name, const std::string& group) const
53 {
54  if (limits_set_ && model_set_)
55  {
56  planning_context = std::make_shared<PlanningContextCIRC>(name, group, model_, limits_);
57  return true;
58  }
59  else
60  {
61  if (!limits_set_)
62  {
63  ROS_ERROR_STREAM("Limits are not defined. Cannot load planning context. "
64  "Call setLimits loadContext");
65  }
66  if (!model_set_)
67  {
68  ROS_ERROR_STREAM("Robot model was not set");
69  }
70  return false;
71  }
72 }
